$t[35] = 'K&euml;t&euml; (d&euml;nim) p&euml;r shkak se ju u tall&euml;t me ajetet e All-llahut, juve u mashtroi jeta e dynjas&euml;. Sot, pra, nuk do t&euml; nxirreni prej tij (zjarrit), e as nuk k&euml;rkohet q&euml; ata t&rsquo;i kthehen pendimit t&euml; All-llahut.';
